Mamelodi Sundowns have been drawn in Group C of the Champions League where they will face AS Vita (DR Congo), St George (Ethiopia) and Esperance (Tunisia).The draw happened today in CAF&#8217;s headquarters in Cairo, Egypt. The defending Champions will face the Ethiopian outfit, St George at home in the weekend of May 12-14.Full draw results:Group A: Ferroviario Beira, El Merrikh, Al Hilal, Etoile du SahelGroup B: Caps United, Ahli Tripoli, USM Alger, ZamalekGroup C: St George, AS Vita, Esperance, Mamelodi SundownsGroup D: Zanaco, Cotton Sport, Wydad Casablanca, Al Ahly-Ntsako Mashaba